title: The Corner Store
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A local Cape Cod landmark located on the Harwich town line. Has vegan options. Offers burritos with organic tempeh (by request), paninis, in-house-made hummus, caramelized onions, grilled eggplant, long-grain brown rice, beans, desserts. Uses no trans fats or hydrogenated oils, MSG, or high fructose corn syrup.
